| DAMAGE format package v1.0

@addfunc+
| display a number as currency — set @var n+(value)-
@print,var+
     +$(n)-
@-
@addfunc:createname"currency"
@---

@addfunc+
| pad a number with leading zeros to 3 digits — set @var n+(value)-
if, (n) < 10
@print,var+
     +00(n)-
@-
if, (n) > 9
if, (n) < 100
@print,var+
     +0(n)-
@-
if, (n) > 99
@print,var+
     +(n)-
@-
@addfunc:createname"pad"
@---
